ETHICAL USE:
This project is built for the security community to:
- Improve defensive capabilities by understanding offensive techniques
- Conduct authorized security assessments professionally
- Advance security research in a responsible manner
- Educate security professionals on modern evasion techniques

If you discover vulnerabilities using this software:
- Follow responsible disclosure practices
- Report to appropriate vendors through official channels
- Do NOT exploit vulnerabilities on unauthorized systems
- Share knowledge with the community ethically

EDUCATIONAL PURPOSE:
This software is intended to educate security professionals about:
- Modern malware development techniques
- EDR/AV evasion methodologies
- Red team operations
- Defensive strategies

Users are expected to apply this knowledge responsibly and legally.

